    "html_format": "<div class=\"document-view-wrapper\">\n<style>\n.html-preview * {font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: 12pt;}\n.html-preview a.NoteRef {text-decoration: none;}\n.html-preview table td {vertical-align: top;}\n.html-preview table {width: 100%;}\n.html-preview p {white-space: pre-wrap;}\n.html-preview .leading {width: 4px; display: inline-block;}\n.html-preview hr {height: 1px; padding: 0; margin: 1em 0; border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #CCC;}\n.html-preview .Normal {className: Normal; margin-bottom: 10pt;}\n.html-preview .a {font-family: 'Calibri';}\n.html-preview .a3 {font-family: 'AntiquaUz'; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;}\n.html-preview .Text {font-family: 'AntiquaUz'; font-size: 12pt;}\n.html-preview .a4 {font-size: 9pt; font-style: italic;}\n.html-preview .a5 {className: a5; text-align: left; margin-bottom: 8pt; text-indent: 48px;}\n</style>\n<div class=\"html-preview\">\n<style>.html-preview{width: 762px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-top: 76px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-bottom: 32px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-left: 81px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-right: 57px}</style><p class=\"a3\" style=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; color: #auto;\">Пул суммалари ва қимматбаҳо қоғозларни депозитга қабул қилиб олиш</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: center;\"><span class=\"structures structure-2\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#2}Нотариус томонидан тасдиқланган сана</span></p>\n<p class=\"a4\" style=\"\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: center;\"><span class=\"structures structure-3\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#3}Нотариус идорасининг манзили</span></p>\n<p class=\"a4\" style=\"\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: center;\"><span class=\"structures structure-4\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#4}Нотариус (нотариал идоранинг) Ф.И.О</span></p>\n<p class=\"a4\" style=\"\"></p>\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\" text-align: center; margin-top: 5.65pt; margin-bottom: 5.65pt; text-indent: 66px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; color: #auto;\">К<span class=\"leading\"></span>В И Т А Н Ц И Я ____-сон</span></p>\n<p class=\"a3\" style=\" text-align: center; margin-top: 5.65pt; margin-bottom: 5.65pt; text-indent: 37px;\"><span class=\"structures structure-5\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; color: #auto;\">{#5}Квитанция берилган сана</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Қабул қилиб олган: </span><span class=\"structures structure-7\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#7}Қабул қилиб олган шахснинг Ф.И.О </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> (паспорт </span><span class=\"structures structure-8\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#8}Қабул қилиб олган шахснинг паспорт серия рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">,<span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span class=\"structures structure-9\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#9}Қабул қилиб олган шахсга паспорт берилган ҳудуд</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span>томонидан </span><span class=\"structures structure-10\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#10}Қабул қилиб олган шахснинг паспорт берилган сана</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> йилда берилган).</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Яшаш манзили: </span><span class=\"structures structure-11\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#11}Қабул қилиб олган шахснинг яшаш манзили</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">,<span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span class=\"structures structure-15\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#15}Қабул қилиб олган шахснинг яшаётган хонадон рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">-хонадон.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Кимнинг номига топширилади: </span><span class=\"structures structure-17\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#17}Ҳужжат топширадиган шахснинг Ф.И.О</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> (паспорт </span><span class=\"structures structure-18\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#18} Ҳужжат топширадиган шахснинг паспорт серия рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">,<span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span class=\"structures structure-19\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#19}Ҳужжат топширадиган шахсга паспорт берилган ҳудуд</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> ИИБ томонидан </span><span class=\"structures structure-20\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#20}Ҳужжат топширадиган шахсга паспорт берилган сана</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> йилда берилган).</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Яшаш манзили: </span><span class=\"structures structure-21\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#21}Ҳужжат топширадиган шахснинг яшаш манзили</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">,<span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span class=\"structures structure-24\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#24}Ҳужжат топширадиган шахснинг яшаш уйнинг рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">-уй.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Тўлов қайси мажбуриятлар ёки тўловлар бўйича келиб тушган: </span><span class=\"structures structure-25\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#25}Нотариус идорасининг манзили</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> </span><span class=\"structures structure-30 structure-32\" style=\"className:30 32; font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#30}Давлат нотариал идорасининг рақами</span><span class=\"structures structure-30\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#30} </span><span class=\"structures structure-30 structure-30\" style=\"className:30 30; font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#30}давлат нотариал идораси</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> </span><span class=\"structures structure-31\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; display: none;\">{#31}хусусий нотариал идора нотариуси </span><span class=\"structures structure-33\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#33}Нотариуснинг Ф.И.О </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> томонидан </span><span class=\"structures structure-26\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#26}Қарз шартномаси тасдиқланган сана</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> да </span><span class=\"structures structure-27\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#27}Қарз шартномасининг қайд қилинган реестр рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> реестр рақами билан тасдиқланган қарз шартномаси.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Депозитга қабул қилинган пул маблағи: </span><span class=\"structures structure-28\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#28}Депозитга қабул қилинган пул маблағи суммаси</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> сўм.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Реестрга ______________-сон билан қайд қилинди.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Давлат божи: _________ сўм (_________________) ундирилди.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\"\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: center; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 30.266666666667px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Нотариус <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"